{"id": "1195200671532716102", "channel_id": "1193425558286114826", "type": 0, "author_id": "857891931253374986", "author_name": "jojosir.", "author_bot": false, "content": "本质上是一个三启角色变成了另一个三启角色", "timestamp": "2024-01-12T03:00:45.848000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1193425558286114826", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "採訪校貓區", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1195202133742587944", "channel_id": "1193425558286114826", "type": 0, "author_id": "857891931253374986", "author_name": "jojosir.", "author_bot": false, "content": "60抽你可以说很少，也可以说很多。关键是，凭什么要把抽拿去填新开的洞？普池角色启灵，命轮，万用启灵不要了吗？\n现在看起来这个角色能借，非必须，但是只要开了这个洞，策划有的是法子让你不得不去换。网游有很多先例，你游策划的公信力也不是那么足。", "timestamp": "2024-01-12T03:06:34.466000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1193425558286114826", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "採訪校貓區", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
